266
00:20:57,470 --> 00:21:00,894
The NPO you work for.

267
00:21:22,437 --> 00:21:23,481
[Ogami] Thank you.

268
00:21:23,565 --> 00:21:25,234
-Welcome.
-Take the luggage, please.

269
00:21:25,318 --> 00:21:26,320
Yes, sir.

270
00:21:28,407 --> 00:21:30,621
-[staff 1] Welcome.
-[staff 2] Welcome.

271
00:21:30,704 --> 00:21:32,750
[staff 1 gasps]
We've been waiting for you, Madam.

272
00:21:32,833 --> 00:21:34,587
-Long time no see.
-[staff 1] Come in.

273
00:21:37,425 --> 00:21:41,058
