274
00:21:57,883 --> 00:21:59,010
[in English] You good?

275
00:22:00,722 --> 00:22:02,308
I thought I was doing some good.

276
00:22:03,562 --> 00:22:05,314
Maybe he wasn't telling the truth.

277
00:22:06,651 --> 00:22:08,154
Doesn't have a reason to lie.

278
00:22:10,158 --> 00:22:13,915
The farmer was alleging fraud.
It's not something we can leave alone.

279
00:22:15,251 --> 00:22:18,925
Well you're an insider now.
You have access to information at the NPO.

280
00:22:21,179 --> 00:22:22,182
Hey.

281
00:22:22,683 --> 00:22:24,019
