[Ryu exhales sharply]

294
00:23:05,852 --> 00:23:08,984
Japan is one of the safest places
in the world.

295
00:23:10,027 --> 00:23:11,614
If you mind your own business.

296
00:23:13,576 --> 00:23:16,874
If you get involved,
it's one of the most dangerous.

297
00:23:18,503 --> 00:23:22,720
'Cause no one will help you
once the tides are against you.

298
00:23:35,579 --> 00:23:37,708
[phone ringing]

299
00:23:41,423 --> 00:23:42,425
[ringing stops]

300
00:23:55,493 --> 00:23:59,000
