307
00:24:22,840 --> 00:24:24,844
Is it something I can help with?

308
00:24:25,512 --> 00:24:26,931
Please go see her.

309
00:24:28,225 --> 00:24:32,066
She started working
at her friend's flower shop.

310
00:24:32,651 --> 00:24:33,778
Flower shop?

311
00:24:34,362 --> 00:24:38,955
She's the most mature out of the four,
but that's because she keeps it all in.

312
00:24:42,713 --> 00:24:44,717
Be sure to talk to her.

313
00:24:46,303 --> 00:24:47,471
