<i>I cannot take your call right now</i> --

316
00:25:07,721 --> 00:25:08,723
[beeps]

317
00:25:11,228 --> 00:25:13,482
[ringing]

318
00:25:14,777 --> 00:25:16,154
How about this?

319
00:25:16,238 --> 00:25:17,574
[customer] It's so pretty.

320
00:25:18,116 --> 00:25:20,246
