323
00:25:25,089 --> 00:25:27,134
[Yumiko] <i>I cannot take your call</i> --

324
00:25:27,218 --> 00:25:28,220
[beeps]

325
00:25:29,264 --> 00:25:30,892
[phone rings]

326
00:25:31,393 --> 00:25:32,436
