As I mentioned before,
the Japanese reporters are not safe.

331
00:25:43,083 --> 00:25:44,168
Do not trust them.

332
00:25:45,129 --> 00:25:48,385
All righty, I gotcha.
What do you have for me now?

333
00:25:49,053 --> 00:25:51,141
And that murder of Takeuchi's son,

334
00:25:51,892 --> 00:25:54,732
that did not go down
like everything was reported.

335
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:58,405
The mother of the guy was saying
he didn't commit suicide.

336
00:25:58,488 --> 00:26:02,163
I mean, committing suicide?
That's a fucking joke. He was murdered.

337
00:26:02,914 --> 00:26:04,125
How do you know this?

338
00:26:04,208 --> 00:26:06,046
<i>Everyone knows this!</i>

339
00:26:06,129 --> 00:26:09,720
Not everyone, come on. I need evidence.

340
00:26:09,803 --> 00:26:11,724
[laughs]

341
00:26:11,807 --> 00:26:14,020
