342
00:26:14,103 --> 00:26:16,483
So how am I meant to write
a story about this?

343
00:26:17,068 --> 00:26:18,988
<i>Expose the man behind everything.</i>

344
00:26:20,366 --> 00:26:23,706
The man who makes the orders. The Owl.

345
00:26:29,467 --> 00:26:31,555
-[Sheena, in Japanese] Red.
-[Risako] Red.

346
00:26:34,018 --> 00:26:35,605
[Sheena] Hmm.

347
00:26:35,688 --> 00:26:37,149
Not red.

348
00:26:38,443 --> 00:26:41,534
