485
00:37:19,558 --> 00:37:21,854
Tell me! Who is she?

486
00:37:21,938 --> 00:37:23,273
Say it!

487
00:37:23,357 --> 00:37:27,031
Who is it? Who is it? Who is it?

488
00:37:27,115 --> 00:37:29,494
Tell me! Who is she?

489
00:37:29,578 --> 00:37:30,580
Hey!

490
00:37:30,664 --> 00:37:32,668
[panting]

491
00:37:33,628 --> 00:37:37,385
